## helpers

since
: 1.0.0

Add all the marscss helpers and pass their arguments

~~~scss
@include style(helpers());
~~~


## customize helpers

You have a group of variables within default-variables to adjust the prefixes and colors of the helpers globally.

<%= code_snippet('helpers',
                 "#{config.marscss_path}/core/_default-variables.scss") %>


