## helpers-columns

since
: 1.0.0

arguments
  : `$prefix`: `$prefix-helper-columns` *[string]*
  : `$sizes`: `$helper-columns-sizes` *[(name: size)]*

Add a helper for the containers to work your children as columns of the same size from a certain size

~~~scss
@include style(helpers-columns());
~~~

<% example_html do %>
<div class="columns-sm">
  <div>1</div>
  <div>2</div>
  <div>3</div>
</div>
<div class="columns-md">
  <div>1</div>
  <div>2</div>
  <div>3</div>
  <div>4</div>
</div>
<% end %>


